== Description == <!--T:11-->

<!--T:3-->
The [[Image:Draft_Snap_Endpoint.svg|24px]] '''Draft Snap Endpoint''' option snaps to the endpoints of edges. The edges can belong to [[Draft_Workbench|Draft]] or [[BIM_Workbench|BIM]] objects but also to objects created with other [[Workbenches|workbenches]].

